        <li>
          All MA's have a deadline, assignments handed in, in due time, are
          given feedback, late deliveries are not
        </li>
        <li>
          Technically, you can hand in the MA's when you start your exam project
          <ul><li>BUT DON'T WAIT THAT LONG</li></ul>
        </li>
        <li>There is a total of 4 MA's</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
